	Laxmi Pooja Masala incense sticks have a blissfully heady aroma which is ideal for helping to unwind after a busy day and bringing a level of balance. These incense sticks are hand rolled and are made using traditional natural ingredients with a recipe handed down through generations. This exotic perfume is made up of sandalwood, aromatic roots, herbs, natural oils, lavender and bergamot orange to deliver a truly astounding fragrance. This box of cored incense sticks contains approx 20 incense sticks, each stick burns for approx. 30 mins. The packaging is now eco friendly and 100% recyclable.</p>
